content.title: Socially Responsible
content.excerpt: The companies of tomorrow: a manifesto
content.article_text:
Our services are provided via two companies: “RedLaboro” and “Capital Becario”. The corporate government is the same for both of them, but they have different legal representations. Part of our strategy involves no public knowledge that these companies are “brothers” ( or parent-child companies), but rather partners.

The IT branch also acts as an independent entity. This one is called “Smartbooms”. Smartbooks provides IT services to both, RedLaboro and Capital Becarios.

RedLaboro is a specialized job search engine for internship positions ONLY. There are two types of users in this system: students (applicants looking for an internship) and Companies (recruiters). We want to add a third kind of user: the universities (so they can make queries, see charts and reports about the behavior of their students in the real-world environment).

For the Students interface the only “innovation” we introduced was the “Visual Management of the Student’s Availability”: nothing more than a clickable table where the user activates the hours he’s not available to work in the internship (see photo no.1). The applicant also chooses the validity period of that specific schedule.

content.title: A Comic Adventure
content.excerpt: Did you know Hellboy has a brother? Neither did we
content.article_text:
Few games have become as popular as the Clash of Clans Franchise game for Android. The original game was released in 1997 and caused a storm when it hit the shelves, as it provided gamers with a way of causing havoc in a top down city environment that no one had ever seen before. The game has developed over the years but The Clash of Clans Hack Tool for iPad and Android remains the same, players get to commit crimes, work for gangs and treat the city as their playground. killing, stealing and committing terror in the city is encouraged in the game and players are rewarded for being ruthless.

The latest news is Clash of Clans takes the game into a fully realized three dimensional world where almost anything is possible. The games features a large number of gems hack and missions which allows foe the player to control several different characters. The game also features a large selection of mini games, such as Tennis, Golf and Mountain biking. Everything in the www.clashofclanshack.fr is also extremely customizable, from the vehicles that one can access through out the game, to the clothes that the individual payers wear.

A multiplayer game mode has been included in this latest edition and features a selection of interesting game hacks and cheats that can be played between friends on one console, or via the web with other players through out the world. This latest version really does cram in as much as possible, becoming a virtual world for gamers to enjoy for hours at a time. The original Clash of Clans Hack is a vast code that should keep fans of the franchise entertained for a long time to come.

content.title: Superman: A review
content.excerpt: Big in scope, dense in story, and pivotal to the Marvel Cinematic Universe as a whole.
content.article_text:
Captain America: The Winter Soldier is a big movie. Big in scope, dense in story, and pivotal to the Marvel Cinematic Universe as a whole. It continues the story of Steve Rogers (Chris Evans), also known as Captain America, as he begins to return to “normal” life after saving the world with some friends in The Avengers. He’s joined by fellow S.H.I.E.L.D. agent Natasha Romanoff (Scarlett Johansson), director Nick Fury (Samuel L. Jackson), a soldier turned friend Sam Wilson (Anthony Mackie) and a slew of others including, but not limited to, characters played by Sebastian Stan, Robert Redford, Frank Grillo, Georges St. Pierre, Cobie Smulders and Hayley Atwell. Like I said, it’s a big movie.

Facts:

  1. one
  2. two
  3. three 
  4. four
  5. five

Directors Anthony and Joe Russo do a solid job of molding all these moving parts into a story that, for the most part, makes sense. But even when the story gets a little too complicated and the exposition a bit too wordy, it’s quickly saved by its entertaining action and continual narrative twists. Many of these will change everything you thought you knew about the Marvel Cinematic Universe. And I’m not just talking about the two credits scenes. Captain America: The Winter Soldier is a fun, worthy, if slightly bulky entry in the Marvel Cinematic Universe.
content.Author: German Loussiere
